# 📰 Fake News Detector

A Machine Learning based web application that detects whether a news article is **Fake** or **Real** using Natural Language Processing (NLP) techniques and multiple classification algorithms.

---

## 🚀 Features

- Detects fake and real news instantly
- NLP based text preprocessing
- Machine Learning classification models
- User-friendly web interface
- Real-time prediction system
- Flask web deployment

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- Python
- Flask
- Scikit-learn
- Pandas
- NumPy
- HTML/CSS
- NLP
- Machine Learning

---

## 📊 Machine Learning Models Used

The project uses multiple ML algorithms for prediction:

- Logistic Regression
- Decision Tree Classifier
- Gradient Boosting Classifier
- Random Forest Classifier

---

## 🧠 NLP Techniques Used

- Text Cleaning
- Lowercasing
- Punctuation Removal
- URL Removal
- Regular Expressions
- TF-IDF Vectorization

